      "title": "Ranil \u2013 Basil meeting today (17)",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Sri Lankan President Ranil Wickremesinghe and Former Minister Basil Rajapaksa, who is also the National Organizer of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna are expected to meet on Thursday (18).",
        "A senior spokesman of the SLPP told News First that the meeting is set to take place at the President's Office.",
        "It is reported that the current situation in the country, as well as plans to implement a new government in the future, are among the topics to be discussed."
      ],
